            <para><guimenu>Description:</guimenu> Enable &abbrev; to run in multithreaded mode and use multiple CPUs. Available only in <phrase condition="pe">&product; 4 F1</phrase><phrase condition="ose">&product; 3.3</phrase> and later. See <xref linkend="chapter-multithreading"/> for details.</para>
